reviewText: LIFE HAS MORE MEANING WHEN YOU KNOW THE TRUTH ABOUT IT AND WHAT YOU DONT KNOW MAY KILL NOT ONLY YOU BUT AN ENTIRE NATION!!!

I've never been much of a conspiracy theorist. But watching this riveting DVD about the alien phenomenon really sparked my interest in extraterrestrial life and related mysteries of the world. In fact, It has made me wonder if the men in black have been trying to hide the truth about aliens from us all along.

One of the most fascinating documentaries I have ever seen!

Wow! This author really hits home with many of the suspicions that I had.  I now know we are not here alone.  Highly recommend if you are questioning if their are extraterrestrial beings.  Jimmy Cruse really hits it out of the park with Secret Scandals.
